        <!-- ===== CONNECTIONS =====
          Strategy: All wires approach each UC from the LEFT side (target x=345,570,795).
          They travel through the inter-column GAPS only (not inside any column).

          Gap columns (no UC vertices):
            gap01 (actors→col1): x=65~119
            gap12 (col1→col2):   x=276~344
            gap23 (col2→col3):   x=501~569
            gap34 (col3→col4):   x=726~794

          Each wire gets its own unique x-offset in the gap so vertical segments don't overlap.
          Wires go: actor → down to a y-corridor at bottom (y=620~860) → right through gaps → up to target UC y-center.

          UC y-centers (y+25):
            col1: uc001=105, uc002=170, uc003=235, uc004=300, uc005=365
            col2: uc006=105, uc007=170, uc008=235, uc009=300, uc010=365, uc011=430, uc012=495, uc013=560
            col3: uc014=105, uc015=170, uc016=235, uc017=300, uc018=365
            col4: uc019=105, uc020=170, uc021=235, uc022=300, uc023=365, uc024=430, uc025=495
        -->

